title: Spaghetti Carbonara
summary: Spaghetti Carbonara is an Italian classic that everyone should know how to make. It's simple yet delicious, with creamy sauce, crispy pancetta, and plenty of Parmesan cheese. This recipe is perfect for a quick weeknight dinner or a cozy weekend meal.

title: Caprese Salad
summary: Caprese Salad is a refreshing and vibrant salad made with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, basil, and a drizzle of balsamic glaze. It's perfect as a side dish or a light lunch on a warm summer day.

title: Grilled Salmon with Avocado Salsa
summary: Grilled Salmon with Avocado Salsa is a fresh and healthy dish that's perfect for summer grilling. The salmon is seasoned with spices and grilled to perfection, then topped with a flavorful avocado salsa. It's a delicious and nutritious meal that's ready in just 20 minutes.

title: Mediterranean Quinoa Salad
summary: Mediterranean Quinoa Salad is a fresh and vibrant salad packed with Mediterranean flavors. It's made with quinoa, cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, olives, and feta cheese, tossed in a tangy lemon vinaigrette. This salad is perfect as a side dish or a light lunch.

title: Chicken Parmesan
summary: Chicken Parmesan is a classic Italian-American dish that's easy to make and incredibly satisfying. Tender chicken breasts are breaded, fried, and topped with marinara sauce and melted mozzarella cheese. Serve it over pasta for a hearty and delicious meal.

title: Avocado Toast with Eggs
summary: Avocado Toast with Eggs is a simple yet delicious breakfast or brunch option. Toasted bread is topped with mashed avocado and a perfectly cooked egg. It's nutritious, filling, and ready in just 15 minutes.

title: Crispy Baked Chicken Wings
summary: Crispy Baked Chicken Wings are a healthier alternative to fried wings. They're coated in a flavorful seasoning mix and baked until crispy and golden brown. Serve them with your favorite dipping sauce for a delicious appetizer or main dish.

title: Vegetable Stir Fry
summary: Vegetable Stir Fry is a quick and easy dish that's perfect for busy weeknights. It's loaded with colorful vegetables stir-fried to perfection in a savory sauce. Serve it over rice or noodles for a satisfying and healthy meal.

title: Homemade Margherita Pizza
summary: Homemade Margherita Pizza is a classic Italian pizza topped with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and basil. It's simple yet delicious, with a crispy crust and gooey cheese. This recipe is perfect for pizza night at home!

title: Berry Spinach Salad with Maple Vinaigrette
summary: Berry Spinach Salad with Maple Vinaigrette is a vibrant and refreshing salad made with baby spinach, fresh berries, and a sweet maple vinaigrette dressing. It's perfect as a side dish or a light lunch on a warm summer day.

title: Shrimp Scampi
summary: Shrimp Scampi is a classic Italian-American dish featuring tender shrimp in a garlic butter sauce. It's quick and easy to make, perfect for a weeknight dinner or a special occasion.
